dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-11T08:30:41.000Z","msg":"剛在香港大學幼兒教育系畢業的張小姐，就希望可以加入警隊的保護兒童組。她表示過去曾經參與制服隊伍，發現自己對幫助市民有熱誠，並且曾參加警隊學長計劃，對督察的工作感到興趣，因而前來投考見習督察一職。<br />\n<br />\n退休警司朱經緯早前被控在2014年期間用警棍襲擊途人，被判襲擊罪成並判囚。張小姐認為，朱經緯案件是個別事件，「相信仲有99%督察、警察都做得非常好，我非常欣賞。」她又提到，若通過遴選將有9個月的督察訓練，而且警隊有內部守則，有信心可面對及化解衝突。"},{"pid":"9d2e6dafb6fed18efae61bd0d2d0d46a7fdaab76","tid":2198241,"uid":222970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-11T08:31:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZymxcE8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZymxcE8.png&h=ea9fb40f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Dn961yu.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDn961yu.png&h=f2fd9c74&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b9cb10ec5d978a910e7440a64074411ef4e44970","tid":2198241,"uid":165749,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9b7b9d4e6ebf93fba37f130a8ad9c5f6cb932095","tid":2198241,"uid":228047,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-11T08:06:06.000Z","msg":"諗極都吾明，明明個頭好勇武，直頭好有鬥志，轉個頭又走去考PI？<br />\n<br />\n到底係什麼因素驅使人甘做？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-11T09:43:41.000Z","msg":"係錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5eb8e139df5c4ce4598b1280215b35dfc56a5e83","tid":2198241,"uid":228047,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"8fb67202ea73211a2c6739214a718adf01ea5c6d","tid":2198241,"uid":214644,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-11T08:07:51.000Z","msg":"錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-11T09:45:49.000Z","msg":"又係錢的問題？當時的骨氣同尊嚴去左邊到！<br />\n<br />\n他們不是有人長期照住，或者已經有哂後備計劃才去做的嗎？"},{"pid":"461f0719fa678dc23aea4adc8ddfba8dc1862c9b","tid":2198241,"uid":315191,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-11T09:47:00.000Z","msg":"識佢地本人，好黃"},{"pid":"af249df9196868a8c72bb57f5bbbacd1e9f34a32","tid":2198241,"uid":16775,"like":0,"